* [[Kelly Hu]] voices [[Cheshire (comics)|Cheshire]] &nbsp;&ndash; Hu previously worked with Weisman in [[The Spectacular Spider-Man (TV series)|''The Spectacular Spider-Man'']] as well as voice acting in ''Batman: Under the Red Hood''.<ref name=IGN2>{{cite web|last=Goldman|first=Eric|title=Kelly Hu Takes on Hawaii Five-0|url=http://tv.ign.com/articles/113/1131283p1.html|work=Television/Previews|publisher=IGN.com|accessdate=21 October 2011}}</ref>

* [[Rob Lowe]] voices [[Captain Marvel (DC Comics)|Captain Marvel]] &nbsp;&ndash; Considered by ''[[IGN]]'' to be "the best superhero guest-voicing turn in some time. (Lowe) plays him like your goofy uncle (or little cousin?) who's trying way too hard to fit in with the cool kids. "I'm really looking forward to hanging with you guys," he blurts out with unabashed enthusiasm".<ref name=IGN1>{{cite web|last=Collura|first=Scott|title=Young Justice: "Alpha Male" Review Or, why'd you screw us over, Aqualad?|url=http://tv.ign.com/articles/119/1199030p1.html|work=Television/Reviews|publisher=IGN.com|accessdate=21 October 2011}}</ref> Weisman notes that the character "will be an important recurring character in the series, so this could ultimately involve multiple episodes for Lowe."<ref name=TVG1>{{cite web|last=Sands|first=Rich|title=Exclusive: Rob Lowe Lands a Marvel-ous Gig on Young Justice|url=http://www.tvguide.com/News/Exclusive-Rob-Lowe-1020825.aspx|work=Today's News: Our Take|publisher=TVGuide|accessdate=21 October 2011}}</ref>

* [[Vanessa Marshall]] voices [[Black Canary]] - Series co-creator [[Greg Weisman]] has said her role on the show was in part because she is his favorite character in the DC universe.{{cn|date=November 2011}}

